## Component Licenses

This dataset incorporates annotations built upon materials from various sources, each under its own license. The original images and data are NOT included in this repository and remain under their original licenses.

### 1. Visual Genome
- **License:** Apache License, Version 2.0
- **Source:** https://homes.cs.washington.edu/~ranjay/visualgenome/
- **Full license:** https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

### 2. Flickr30K
- **License:** CC0 1.0 Universal (Public Domain Dedication)
- **Source:** http://shannon.cs.illinois.edu/DenotationGraph/
- **Full license:** https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/

### 3. FGVC-Aircraft
- **License:** Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-SA 4.0)
- **Source:** https://www.robots.ox.ac.uk/~vgg/data/fgvc-aircraft/
- **Full license:** https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

### 4. DTD (Describable Textures Dataset)
- **License:** Apache License, Version 2.0
- **Source:** https://www.robots.ox.ac.uk/~vgg/data/dtd/
- **Full license:** https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

### 5. EuroSAT
