## Why CC BY-SA 4.0?

The FGVC-Aircraft dataset is licensed under CC BY-SA 4.0, which requires that derivative works be distributed under the same or a compatible license. Since our annotations reference FGVC-Aircraft data, the ShareAlike condition applies. CC BY-SA 4.0 is compatible with the Apache 2.0 and CC0 licenses of the other source datasets.

---

## Note on INQUIRE

INQUIRE annotations are NOT included in this repository due to INQUIRE's CC BY-NC 4.0 license, which restricts commercial use. We provide scripts to independently generate INQUIRE-based annotations. Users who do so must comply with INQUIRE's license terms (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/).

